I mean, you go to slay the dragon, at least in part, because of the riches the dragon has.  In order to get to the dragon, you have to beat her minions.  That is missing, for the most part, in EQ.  Boss mobs should drop MORE items.  And they should be level appropriate.  And they should have level restrictions, but not NO DROP (I mean, what's the use of adventuring, if you can't sell the loot you don't want/need?).<br>
